				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Holy Fuck, he hit it right on the nose.
<br />

<br />
The first two paragraphs you don't see clearly until you stop playing.
<br />

<br />
When I finally decided to stop playing for just a few months I realized how crappy the game I had been playing for 2-3 years had been and wondered why I kept playing.  Then when I played one day, it pulled be back in for a few more days, and I would still be playing if I hadn't pressed the cancel button on my account before I started again.  And I realized, the only reason I kept on playing was my friends in game.<br />_________________<br />[64 Arch Mage] Shakro Darksummoner (Dark Elf) -Tarew Marr-
