<br />

<br />

<br />
In the end, you should note that it's a game. Quit it's no longer fulfulling the functions of a game in your life. If you have a problem with the service, no one is keeping you in EQ... leave. And if your staying...<br />_________________<br />"The ability to quote is a serviceable substitute for wit."
